%%HP: T(3)A(D)F(.);
\<<
"KREIS GES. MIT TAN-
GENTE
K:(x-u)^2+(y-v)^2=r^2
P: P(Xo/Yo)
INPUT u,v,r,Xo,Yo
OUTPUT T1:M1,Q1
       T2:M2,Q2"
DISPHELP \-> U V R Xo
Yo
  \<< U V R MR\->GL 'Xo
-U' EVAL 'Yo-V'
EVAL \-> H1 H2
    \<< H1 H2 'H1*-U+
H2*-V-R^2' EVAL
    \>> KRGE \-> Bx1
By1 Bx2 By2
    \<< { HOME
ANALYTGEO ALPER
GERADEN } EVAL Bx1
By1 Xo Yo GGLP Bx2
By2 Xo Yo GGLP {
HOME ANALYTGEO
ALPER KREIS } EVAL
    \>>
  \>>
\>>
